4) TLA+ model aligned to the paper

This is the matching abstract verification model. Save as NexusFusion.tla.

------------------------------ MODULE NexusFusion ------------------------------
EXTENDS Naturals, Reals, TLC
CONSTANTS C_Nexus, TauMin, EMax
VARIABLES E, N, Tau, Mode
Phi == E * N * Tau
TypeOK ==
    /\ E \in Real
    /\ N \in Real
    /\ Tau \in Real
    /\ E >= 0.0
    /\ N >= 0.0
    /\ Tau >= 0.0
    /\ Mode \in {"Idle", "Build", "Fusion", "Collapse"}
Init ==
    /\ E = 0.1
    /\ N = 0.1
    /\ Tau = 0.1
    /\ Mode = "Build"
BuildStep ==
    /\ Mode = "Build"
    /\ E' \in Real /\ E' >= E
    /\ N' \in Real /\ N' >= N
    /\ Tau' \in Real /\ Tau' >= Tau
    /\ IF E' * N' * Tau' >= C_Nexus
          THEN Mode' = "Fusion"
          ELSE Mode' = "Build"
FusionStep ==
    /\ Mode = "Fusion"
    /\ E' \in Real /\ E' >= 0.0
    /\ N' \in Real /\ N' >= 0.0
    /\ Tau' \in Real /\ Tau' >= 0.0
    /\ IF Tau' <= TauMin \/ E' >= EMax
          THEN Mode' = "Collapse"
          ELSE /\ Mode' = "Fusion"
               /\ E' * N' * Tau' >= C_Nexus
CollapseRecovery ==
    /\ Mode = "Collapse"
    /\ E' \in Real /\ E' >= 0.0
    /\ N' \in Real /\ N' >= 0.0
    /\ Tau' \in Real /\ Tau' >= 0.0
    /\ IF Tau' > TauMin /\ E' < EMax
          THEN Mode' = "Build"
          ELSE Mode' = "Collapse"
Next ==
    BuildStep \/ FusionStep \/ CollapseRecovery
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_<<E, N, Tau, Mode>>
FusionInvariant ==
    [](Mode = "Fusion" => Phi >= C_Nexus)
SafetyInvariant ==
    [](E >= 0.0 /\ N >= 0.0 /\ Tau >= 0.0)
=============================================================================

And a simple config file NexusFusion.cfg:

SPECIFICATION Spec
CONSTANTS
C_Nexus = 1.0
TauMin = 0.2
EMax = 10.0
INVARIANTS
TypeOK
SafetyInvariant
FusionInvariant

